response.overview: After stumbling on a huge supply of pot, Baby Bash and Chingo Bling hit the road for a munchies-filled journey from Texas to California and back and get mixed up with some of the biggest names in the Latin rap world. Stops on the long, strange trip include a tour of R&D Studios in Albuquerque, N.M., a smoke session with Kid Frost in Las Vegas, and backstage access at a Baby Bash and DJ Kane concert in Corpus Christi, Texas.
